        Creates a new Algorithm instance. The given data is checked for validity.
        Parameters:
        absorptionTime - carbohydrate absorption time
        insulinDuration - insulin duration
        peak - duration in minutes until insulin action reaches it’s peak activity level
        profile - user profile
        glucoseMeasurements - glucose measurements
        bolusTreatments - bolus treatments
        basalTreatments - raw basal treatments
